---
description: Best practices for Next.js applications using the App Router
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: false
---
- Favor React Server Components (RSC) for better performance and SEO
- Use the App Router for improved routing and data fetching
- Implement proper error boundaries with `error.tsx` files
- Use `loading.tsx` for loading states and Suspense for client components
- Optimize images with `next/image` and prioritize WebP format
